      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ALL MUCKED UP (3) found some support last start but struggled into fourth (19.98), beaten 6 lengths. Was in the money the start prior. Key runner on his best form. MY DEAR FRIEND (2) comes off an average performance last start when sixth at Sandown over 515m behind Doongalla Serena (30.38) in a Grade 5. Was a winner prior to that. The form out of his last race has been franked. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. KODA (1) had been racing well with a Mix 6/7 win three back then placed next time before missing the frame latest at Shepparton. Can find the frame this time. BABY BEETS (6) is always hard to beat when he races at this trip.",
